title: Eye Liner, Spiced Chocolate 30
description: Neutrogena Nourishing Eyeliner defines and brightens eyes with luminous color. Subtle light diffusers make the whites of eyes appear whiter, while rich color nourishes skin with Olive Oil and Rainforest Shea Butter. The builtin sharpener gives precise definition and the contoured smudger softens and blends for a variety of looks. Infused with olive oil and rainforest shea butter to condition the delicate skin around your lashes Creamy automatic pencil glides on smoothly, then transforms into longlasting finish that won't budge.

title: L'Oreal Paris Lineur Intense Brush Tip Liquid Eyeliner, Black, 0.24 Ounces
description: Stand out with a dramatically bold or sleek look. Lineur intense brush tip liquid eyeliner has a tapered natural brush that allows you to create the most precise lines for your desired eye looks. Now available in our most intense shade - carbon black.

title: Delon 100% Cotton Rounds - New and Improved Premium Quality Softer Edges - 800 Rounds
description: Delon Premium Cotton Rounds are made in Germany from the finest selection of premium cotton fibers. New & Improved they have softer edges and contain Aloe Vera and Pro-vitamin B5. They retain their shape, are more absorbent, shred less while being extra soft. 8 bags of 100 count each total 800 rounds Packaged in resealable Enviro-friendly bags of 100.
